media:group.media:title: Befunge - The 2d programming language
media:group.media:description:
Wagwanin everybody, thanks for tuning back in. 
I'm starting a mini-series here on esolangs and this inaugural episode will be on the legendary 2d esolang itself, Befunge. Created in '93 befunge unlocks a whole new dimension to your programming toolset. 

Links: 
Befunge on esolangs wiki:
https://esolangs.org/wiki/Befunge
Befunge docs (from the creator himself)
https://catseye.tc/view/Befunge-93/doc/Befunge-93.markdown
Befunge programs by Nautilus (where I got the fibonacci inspiration)
https://github.com/nautilor/befunge/blob/master/examples/fibonacci.bf
